{"tid":1045454,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"超快！傳 AirPods 2 無線充電只需 15 分鐘即可充滿？","createTime":"2019-03-03T15:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T13:21:25.000Z","uid":109383,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2840b753a5aceb047efeac1b10f5962f8f7e6856","tid":1045454,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:11:30.000Z","msg":"來自 @mweinbachXDA Max Weinback 的消息，新的 AirPods 2 的無線充電速度相當驚人，由 0% 充電，只需 15 分鐘便可達 100% 。這速度是要 AirPods 2 及最新的無線電盒配合下才可實現，應該會使用 Qi 無線充電制式。不過缺點方面，充電盒子會較第一代 AirPods 大及重。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，Apple 有機會在 3 月 25 日發佈會裡推出 AirPods 2 以及 AirPower，並在 3 月 29 日正式開售。不過現時仍未確定，相信多等幾個星期就可以有答案了。根據先前的情報指出，AirPods 2 將提供「黑色」版本、音質與附著性有所改善、加入「嘿！Siri」功能，售價則有可能會來到 200 美元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApple 黑科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93f511da6295ed3a05224df243cfc1100b930c2","tid":1045454,"uid":17765,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"咁撚快 $2000 usd啦不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7c89e773477c90e6be88615b712b059cbb3c23","tid":1045454,"uid":1060,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"一味快左勁左 咁就叫黑科技?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70101403c50b26b5062fc5f3c1cd0e517dc3e7d4","tid":1045454,"uid":109383,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"b93f511da6295ed3a05224df243cfc1100b930c2","tid":1045454,"uid":17765,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"咁撚快 $2000 usd啦不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo